reviewText: I remember watching this all the time as a kid. Still have it somewhere, actually. Even now that I'm much older, I still love Toby Terrier movies. So cute and the songs are pretty catchy. I still find myself singing them in my head even years after the last time I've even seen any of the movies.
Got it quick and fast. It will make my remember when stocking all the more special this Christmas season. Thanks
